s changed to \u201cThe DIGIDHAN Mission will work towards the primary objective of promotion of digital payments in the country and to increase the digital payment acceptance infrastructure\u201d.", "012-listElement": "- Other ammendments as per the new notification includes that the operations of DIGIDHAN Mission setup under the Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology (MeitY) is extended till 31st March 2020 (Para 1.4).", "013-listElement": "- **Amendment Notification** \u2013 To see the Amendment Notification released by MeitY \u2013 [Extension Of DigiDhan Mission](http://meity.gov.in/writereaddata/files/Extension_of_DIGIDHAN_MISSION_Mission.pdf)", "014-normal": "Central govt. is working to devise a new mechanism to monitor regional penetration of digital payments. This could be done through geo-tagging digital payment transactions. To see the complete notification for Digi Dhan Mission \u2013 [Digidhan Mission Notification](http://meity.gov.in/writereaddata/files/Notification%20for%20DigiDhan%20mission.pdf)"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "References", "001-normal": "\u2014 For more details, candidates can visit the official website [meity.gov.in/digidhan](http://meity.gov.in/digidhan)"}}